===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|carmin|lang=fr}}, from irregular {{etyl|ML.|en}} {{term|carminium|lang=la}}, itself from {{etyl|ar|en}} {{term|قرمز||crimson, [[kermes]]|lang=ar|sc=Arab|tr=qirmiz}} (from Sanskrit {{term|कृमिज|tr=kṛmija|lang=sa||produced by worms}}, from {{term|कृमि||worm, insect|sc=Deva|tr=kṛ́mi|lang=sa}}), plus or with influence from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|minium|lang=la}}.

